Intro1
------------------------------------------------------------------------
The ship rumbles as the rocket impacts its stern. The sudden fire alarm howl almost tears your eardrums. You hiss a curse and try to maneuver the damaged vessel out of the danger zone. Futile. The guardian satellite did a good job. The ship is out of control. What were you thinking!? The planet is off-limits!


"Luke, status!" you call desperately as you unfasten the belt. Luke's voice coming from above is his usual calm baritone as he reports the impending destruction of the space ship. "I recommend an immediate evacuation."


"No kidding!" you growl while you strap on the assistant device to your wrist. "Transfer yourself, Luke, we're leaving."


